name: NOPE CHALLENGE
summary: Laugh, jump, or scream—it’s all part of the fun! Face towering heights, creepy crawlies, and robotic murder clowns as you challenge your fears. Don’t “NOPE” out too soon! If you do, retreat to Breather Space with Mr. Peels and Coco to calm your nerves and maybe feed some fish before diving back in. Push your phobia limits, or just have a blast! NOPE CHALLENGE reveals which fear makes your heart race the most!
